{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775846710859,"sessionID":"ses_28749f2f4ffeLUsnYfYJHFuunK","part":{"id":"prt_d78b657a50017AjnrnzI7oGOOp","messageID":"msg_d78b64c04001Q0eZYLe4930tYI","sessionID":"ses_28749f2f4ffeLUsnYfYJHFuunK","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_7f30b645b11b47aaad28b04d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: Define the `AgentRuntime` Custom Resource Definition (CRD) types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` to enable Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration for AI agent workloads. This work establishes the core API surface — `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `AgentRuntimeStatus`, and supporting shared types — that the Workload Manager controller and generated `client-go` library consume.\n6: \n7: ## Scope\n8: \n9: ### In scope\n10: \n11: | Item | Detail |\n12: |------|--------|\n13: | **Package** | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` |\n14: | **API group** | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n15: | **Version** | `v1alpha1` |\n16: | **Types defined** | `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeList`, `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `AgentRuntimeStatus`, `TargetPort`, `ProtocolType`, `SandboxTemplate` |\n17: | **Scheme registration** | `groupversion_info.go`, `register.go` — `GroupVersion`, `SchemeBuilder`, `AddToScheme`, kind constants, `Resource()` helper |\n18: | **Kubebuilder markers** | `+genclient`, `+k8s:deepcopy-gen`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`, `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`, `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced`, `+kubebuilder:printcolumn`, validation/default markers |\n19: | **Code generation** | `controller-gen crd` → `manifests/charts/base/crds/`; `controller-gen object` → `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`; `k8s.io/code-generator` → `client-go/` |\n20: | **Generated client surface** | `AgentRuntimeInterface` (Create/Update/UpdateStatus/Delete/DeleteCollection/Get/List/Watch/Patch), `AgentRuntimeInformer`, `AgentRuntimeLister` |\n21: \n22: ### Out of scope\n23: \n24: - `CodeInterpreter` CRD types (separate AR)\n25: - Workload Manager HTTP API routes and handlers\n26: - Reconciler/controller logic\n27: - Helm chart CRD YAML rendering (consumes output, not produced here)\n28: - RBAC / ServiceAccount definitions\n29: \n30: ## Design\n31: \n32: ### File layout\n33: \n34: | File | Role |\n35: |------|------|\n36: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go` | `+groupName` marker, `GroupVersion`, `SchemeBuilder`, `AddToScheme` |\n37: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` | Kind constants (`AgentRuntimeKind`, `AgentRuntimeListKind`, `AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind`), `SchemeGroupVersion`, `Resource()` helper |\n38: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agent_type.go` | `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeList`, `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `AgentRuntimeStatus` |\n39: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` | `TargetPort`, `ProtocolType`, `SandboxTemplate` |\n40: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` | Auto-generated by `controller-gen object` |\n41: \n42: ### Type definitions\n43: \n44: **`AgentRuntime`** — namespaced CRD with `status` subresource:\n45: \n46: ```go\n47: // +genclient\n48: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n49: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n50: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n51: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n52: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n53: type AgentRuntime struct {\n54:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n55:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n56:     Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n57:     Status AgentRuntimeStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n58: }\n59: ```\n60: \n61: **`AgentRuntimeSpec`** — sandbox template and session constraints:\n62: \n63: ```go\n64: type AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n65:     Ports []TargetPort `json:\"targetPort\"`\n66:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n67:     Template *SandboxTemplate `json:\"podTemplate\" protobuf:\"bytes,1,opt,name=podTemplate\"`\n68:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n69:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n70:     SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,2,opt,name=sessionTimeout\"`\n71:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n72:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n73:     MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,3,opt,name=maxSessionDuration\"`\n74: }\n75: ```\n76: \n77: **`AgentRuntimeStatus`** — condition-based status:\n78: \n79: ```go\n80: type AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n81:     // +optional\n82:     Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n83: }\n84: ```\n85: \n86: **`AgentRuntimeList`**:\n87: \n88: ```go\n89: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n90: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n91: type AgentRuntimeList struct {\n92:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n93:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n94:     Items           []AgentRuntime `json:\"items\"`\n95: }\n96: ```\n97: \n98: **Shared types** (`TargetPort`, `ProtocolType`, `SandboxTemplate`):\n99: \n100: ```go\n101: type ProtocolType string\n102: \n103: const (\n104:     ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n105:     ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n106: )\n107: \n108: type TargetPort struct {\n109:     // +optional\n110:     PathPrefix *string `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n111:     // +optional\n112:     Name *string `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n113:     Port uint32 `json:\"port\"`\n114:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n115:     // +kubebuilder:default=HTTP\n116:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS\n117:     Protocol ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n118: }\n119: \n120: type SandboxTemplate struct {\n121:     // +optional\n122:     Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n123:     // +optional\n124:     Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n125:     Spec corev1.PodSpec `json:\"spec\"`\n126: }\n127: ```\n128: \n129: ### Scheme registration\n130: \n131: **`groupversion_info.go`**:\n132: \n133: ```go\n134: // +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n135: package v1alpha1\n136: \n137: var (\n138:     GroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}\n139:     SchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}\n140:     AddToScheme = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n141: )\n142: ```\n143: \n144: **`register.go`**:\n145: \n146: ```go\n147: var (\n148:     AgentRuntimeKind             = \"AgentRuntime\"\n149:     AgentRuntimeListKind         = \"AgentRuntimeList\"\n150:     AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")\n151: )\n152: \n153: var SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion\n154: \n155: func Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource {\n156:     return GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)\n157: }\n158: ```\n159: \n160: ### Code generation pipeline\n161: \n162: ```\n163: controller-gen crd  → manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml\n164: controller-gen object → pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go\n165: k8s.io/code-generator → client-go/ (clientset, informers, listers, fakes)\n166: ```\n167: \n168: Invocation: `make gen-all` → `generate` (controller-gen) + `gen-client` (`hack/update-codegen.sh`).\n169: \n170: ## Impact analysis\n171: \n172: ### Files created\n173: \n174: | File | Lines (est.) |\n175: |------|-------------|\n176: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go` | ~25 |\n177: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` | ~25 |\n178: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agent_type.go` | ~60 |\n179: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` | ~45 |\n180: \n181: ### Files generated (not hand-edited)\n182: \n183: | File | Tool |\n184: |------|------|\n185: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` | `controller-gen object` |\n186: | `manifests/charts/base/crds/*.yaml` | `controller-gen crd` |\n187: | `client-go/` (entire tree) | `k8s.io/code-generator` |\n188: \n189: ### Downstream consumers\n190: \n191: | Consumer | Dependency |\n192: |----------|-----------|\n193: | `client-go` typed client | Imports `runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime` / `AgentRuntimeList` for CRUD operations |\n194: | `client-go` informers/listers | Uses `AgentRuntimeInformer`, `AgentRuntimeLister` built from these types |\n195: | Workload Manager controller | Imports types for sandbox lifecycle reconciliation |\n196: | Helm chart CRDs | Rendered YAML consumed by `kubectl apply` / Helm install |\n197: | Fake clients | `client-go/.../fake/` test doubles for unit testing |\n198: \n199: ### Breaking change risk\n200: \n201: - **Low**: This is a greenfield type definition. No existing runtime behavior is modified.\n202: - **Future**: Adding required fields to `AgentRuntimeSpec` after initial release will require CRD version bump (`v1alpha1` → `v1alpha2`) and conversion webhook.\n203: \n204: ## Alternatives considered\n205: \n206: ### 1. Standalone CRD YAML (no Go types)\n207: \n208: **Approach**: Write CRD manifests directly as YAML without Go type definitions.\n209: \n210: **Rejected because**: AgentCube uses Go controllers (Workload Manager) that require typed Go structs for serialization, validation, and scheme registration. YAML-only CRDs would force manual JSON unmarshaling and lose compile-time type safety.\n211: \n212: ### 2. Kubebuilder/controller-runtime scaffolding\n213: \n214: **Approach**: Use `kubebuilder create api` to scaffold the full controller + CRD project structure.\n215: \n216: **Rejected because**: AgentCube's Workload Manager is a Gin-based HTTP service, not a controller-runtime manager. The project uses `controller-gen` for type/code generation only, without the controller-runtime manager scaffolding. Adopting Kubebuilder would introduce an unnecessary runtime dependency and project structure mismatch.\n217: \n218: ### 3. Multi-version API from day one (`v1alpha1` + `v1beta1`)\n219: \n220: **Approach**: Define two API versions simultaneously with a conversion webhook.\n221: \n222: **Rejected because**: The project is pre-GA with no existing users. A single `v1alpha1` version is sufficient for initial development. Adding versions and conversion webhooks adds operational complexity without current benefit.\n223: \n224: ### 4. Embed full `corev1.PodTemplateSpec` instead of custom `SandboxTemplate`\n225: \n226: **Approach**: Use `corev1.PodTemplateSpec` directly in `AgentRuntimeSpec` rather than the lighter `SandboxTemplate` wrapper.\n227: \n228: **Rejected because**: `SandboxTemplate` provides a controlled surface — optional `labels`/`annotations` maps with a required embedded `corev1.PodSpec` — while keeping the CRD schema focused on what AgentCube manages. Full `PodTemplateSpec` would expose `ObjectMeta` fields that are not relevant to sandbox template configuration.\n229: \n230: ## Dependencies\n231: \n232: | Dependency | Version | Purpose |\n233: |------------|---------|---------|\n234: | `k8s.io/apimachinery` | `v0.34.1` | `metav1.TypeMeta`, `metav1.ObjectMeta`, `metav1.Duration`, `metav1.Condition`, `schema.GroupVersion` |\n235: | `k8s.io/api` | `v0.34.1` | `corev1.PodSpec` embedded in `SandboxTemplate` |\n236: | `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` | `v0.22.2` | `scheme.Builder` for scheme registration |\n237: | `controller-gen` | `v0.17.2` | CRD YAML and deepcopy generation |\n238: | `k8s.io/code-generator` | `v0.34.1` | client-go library generation |\n239: \n240: ## Verification\n241: \n242: ```bash\n243: # Generate CRD YAML, deepcopy, and client-go\n244: make gen-all\n245: \n246: # Verify no diff (all generated files committed)\n247: make gen-check\n248: \n249: # Validate CRD schema\n250: kubectl apply -f manifests/charts/base/crds/ --dry-run=server\n251: ```\n\n(End of file - total 251 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n\n## Purpose\n\nDefine the `AgentRuntime` Custom Resource Definition (CRD) types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` to enable Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration for AI agent workloads. This work establishes the core API surface — `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `AgentRuntimeStatus`, and supporting shared types — that the Workload Manager controller and generated `client-go` library consume.\n\n## Scope\n\n### In scope\n\n| Item | Detail |\n|------|--------|\n| **Package** | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` |\n| **API group** | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n| **Version** | `v1alpha1` |\n| **Types defined** | `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeList`, `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `AgentRuntimeStatus`, `TargetPort`, `ProtocolType`, `SandboxTemplate` |\n| **Scheme registration** | `groupversion_info.go`, `register.go` — `GroupVersion`, `SchemeBuilder`, `AddToScheme`, kind constants, `Resource()` helper |\n| **Kubebuilder markers** | `+genclient`, `+k8s:deepcopy-gen`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`, `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`, `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced`, `+kubebuilder:printcolumn`, validation/default markers |\n| **Code generation** | `controller-gen crd` → `manifests/charts/base/crds/`; `controller-gen object` → `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`; `k8s.io/code-generator` → `client-go/` |\n| **Generated client surface** | `AgentRuntimeInterface` (Create/Update/UpdateStatus/Delete/DeleteCollection/Get/List/Watch/Patch), `AgentRuntimeInformer`, `AgentRuntimeLister` |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"proposal.md","time":{"start":1775846710833,"end":1775846710856}}}}
